    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age.",
