    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless exterior and a cabin that mirrors its original delivery state, this remains a premier choice for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a standard of preservation that is seldom encountered in the pre-owned market.",
