      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning, showroom-ready shape. It drives like a dream and looks like it just rolled off the lot\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 45900.0,
