    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring a high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero clear-coat failure or panel misalignment. A definitive example for the discerning purist.",
